<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>This is an <bold>extern</bold> variable that is declared in <computeroutput><ref refid="stm32f4__rgb__light_8h" kindref="compound">stm32f4_rgb_light.h</ref></computeroutput>. It represents an array of RGB lights. </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
